dc_title_s: Map of the borough of Woodbury, N.J.
dc_description_s: Shows real-property tracts, building coverage, landowners' names, and proposed streets.|"Woodbury was incorporated as a borough, March 10th A.D. 1854, and its limits defined as described by this map."|Includes text, illustration of court-house, and illustrations of prominent residences.
dc_publisher_s: P.S. Duval & Co., steam lith. press.
